導致出現非預定上移情況，專家認為該升降機長期沒保養。 <br />\n<br />\n耀天工程有限公司和總經理劉慶秋早前共承認「沒有確保升降機工程妥善進行」等4罪，被告公司罰款6.3萬港元，劉則罰款3.3萬港元。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190426/bkn-20190426151051689-0426_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190426%2Fbkn-20190426151051689-0426_00822_001.html&d=tLsEO8KpRnvfRHW%2FlT3TjjsAEF7kNGMxk903cO3jeS8%3D&h=872cf72c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190426/bkn-20190426151051689-0426_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3dd15d37d869a4cfafcb9fdaa59b0a43dc97458a","tid":1126388,"uid":91648,"like":170,"dislike":4,"score":166,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T12:13:24.000Z","msg":"天理何在。"},{"pid":"a8de4ac659994b604e38a10af96727e607b8d979","tid":1126388,"uid":5627,"like":339,"dislike":4,"score":335,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T12:15:08.000Z","msg":"同揸車撞死人性質冇分別<br />\n點解可以唔駛判監"},{"pid":"002ab769a9081dab2d9140ebe2dda0037d957687","tid":1126388,"uid":53498,"like":221,"dislike":3,"score":218,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T12:15:26.000Z","msg":"死人都咁輕,香港依家乜撚嘢事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw,吳茂盛"},{"pid":"b1ca138769073395f87c4c2e69d40f7d4043dbea","tid":1126388,"uid":47222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T12:15:45.000Z","msg":"痴撚線咁都冇事"},{"pid":"8ff6d486703da3c1baf7c86feb200d433b06a780","tid":1126388,"uid":170294,"like":120,"dislike":0,"score":120,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T12:16:56.000Z","msg":"無一條罪係<br />\n檢察不當引致死亡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只有普通當你無檢查 bye"},{"pid":"6d590b1388e3df8793286b7cd815105a50bf6733","tid":1126388,"uid":48334,"like":1,"dislike":28,"score":-27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T12:20:37.000Z","msg":"又唔係謀殺想判幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e6c51275af40de052265bef40703e6ffba04e00","tid":1126388,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T12:23:33.000Z","msg":"呢行真係邊個做"}